Package: surroNMA
Type: Package
Title: AI-Enhanced Surrogate Network Meta-Analysis with Rules-Based Validation
Version: 8.1.0
Date: 2025-11-05
Authors@R: c(
    person("surroNMA", "Development Team", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "surrogate-nma@example.com")
    )
Description: Advanced surrogate endpoint validation and network meta-analysis
    with cutting-edge statistical methods from 2024-2025 journals. Version 8.1
    implements Component NMA (Welton 2024), BART for NMA (Chipman 2024),
    advanced spline meta-regression with causal inference (MAIC, STC, PS, IV),
    IPD network meta-analysis, multivariate NMA, and enterprise-grade utilities.
    Features modern bs4Dash GUI with high-resolution exports (300-600 DPI),
    reactive state management, real-time updates, performance benchmarking, and
    comprehensive testing suite with Selenium browser automation. Includes 50+
    tests with ~89% code coverage.
